e:[["$","title","0",{"children":"ISO 27001 for Startups Companies : Benefits | Wizms"}],["$","meta","1",{"name":"description","content":"Wizms offers ISO 27001 for startups company a much needed competitive edge to get ISO 27001 certification in Dubai, UAE which you have been looking for"}],["$","meta","2",{"name":"keywords","content":"ISO 27001 for Startup Companies"}],["$","meta","3",{"property":"og:title","content":"ISO 27001 for Startups Companies : Benefits | Wizms"}],["$","meta","4",{"property":"og:description","content":"Wizms offers ISO 27001 for startups company a much needed competitive edge to get ISO 27001 certification in Dubai, UAE which you have been looking for"}],["$","meta","5",{"property":"og:url","content":"https://wizms.net/why-should-startups-get-iso-27001-certification"}],["$","meta","6",{"property":"og:type","content":"article"}],["$","meta","7",{"property":"article:published_time","content":"2026-01-02T06:31:43+00:00"}],["$","meta","8",{"name":"twitter:card","content":"summary"}],["$","meta","9",{"name":"twitter:title","content":"ISO 27001 for Startups Companies : Benefits | Wizms"}],["$","meta","10",{"name":"twitter:description","content":"Wizms offers ISO 27001 for startups company a much needed competitive edge to get ISO 27001 certification in Dubai, UAE which you have been looking for"}],["$","link","11",{"rel":"icon","href":"/favicon.ico"}],["$","$L1a","12",{}]]
10:["$","p","9",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Mitigated Risks"}]
11:["$","p","10",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"While few startups may not have concentrated on data and information security which most startups should. The reason for the emphasization to get ISO 27001 certification for the startups is because of the risk of potential harm to the reputation that might occur as a result of inappropriate risk management or security breaches. These sort of incidents might ruin your startup's chances of achieving goals and would severely jeopardize the growth of business development before the startup even began to grow"}]
12:["$","p","11",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"These days, it is uncommon for startups to work in areas where information protection and data security don't seem to be a problem. Handling of information particularly in IT-driven startups is a norm, not the exception. Client information, additionally as a startup’s ability, is the very core of the business which needs ultimate protection. Losing information will simply cost a startup its right to exist, either by infringing laws or by gambling with its customer’s trust."}]
13:["$","p","12",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Competitive Advantage"}]
14:["$","p","13",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Customers, today, are becoming more and more conscious of the worth of their information. News regarding information and data breaches spreads quick. Even before the EU GDPR came into effect, the information handling was already a hot topic."}]
15:["$","p","14",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Every single Customer need their information secure and guarded. So, when deciding which company to select for safeguarding or protecting the data and information, customers most of the times usually tend to go for the most secure choice. Checkout the advantages and disadvantages of ISO 27001 certification in Dubai, UAE"}]
16:["$","p","15",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"You and your startup should consider data security seriously because it has always been a game changer so as to get the attention of customers among the umpteen older and stronger competitors. When decide on getting your startup certified in line with the ISO 27001 standard, founders ought to bear in mind its advantages as this will lead them to subsequent big issue founders have in mind – costs."}]
17:["$","p","16",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Reduced Costs"}]
18:["$","p","17",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Now, you will wonder, how is that the ISO 27001 certification assisting a startup to avoid wasting time and money? ISO 27001 certification in Dubai – or at least implementing the certain process in line with the ISO’s standards – will facilitate your startup cut prices from the very beginning. By utilizing the standard, ISO 27001 certification cost in Dubai, UAE would possibly want less capital to break even. By implementing standards in line with ISO 27001, startups lower the number of incidents. By clearly determining the responsibilities and tasks from the start, workers are trained effectively. Awareness amongst the workers is made and established. When aiming at data security, investment in the processes and – most significantly – workers are the strategic way to decide on. Compared to it, expensive software package solutions to safeguard information are required less often than you would possibly assume."}]
